# Terraform working artifacts — never commit these.
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
crash.log
crash.*.log

# Local variable files (may hold secrets) — commit only the *.example.
terraform.tfvars
*.auto.tfvars
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json
